prodNameC: 巴斯銳 新型隱球菌(未滅菌)
ingredientsDesc:
Latex Cryptococcus: latex particles sensitized with an anti-glycuronoxylomannan antibody (mouse), in a glycine buffer.
Positive control antigen: purified Cryptococcus neoformans capsular polyoside.
Diluent buffer: glycine albumin buffer.
Pronase: 2 vials of lyophilized enzymes (pronase) to be reconstituted in 1 ml of distilled or demineralized water.
Stopping solution: stopping solution (enzymatic inhibitor)
disposable agglutination cards
small disposable sticks
All the reagents contain 0.02% of merthiolate and less than 0.1% of sodium azide.
applicantName: 美商伯瑞股份有限公司台灣分公司
applicantAddr: 台北市松山區南京東路4段126號14樓
efficacy: 定性及半定量檢測人體血清、腦脊髓液、支氣管肺泡洗出物及尿液中Cryptococcus neoformans之莢膜抗原。
